    "spell": {
        "name": "Murmuration",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "The target feels the brush of feathers against its skin and hears screeches in its ears, warning it to keep away from a creature you designate that\u2019s within 30 feet of you when you Cast this Spell (which can include yourself). Once per round, if the target moves closer to the designated creature, it must attempt a Will save or take 1d4 piercing or sonic damage.",
